00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:28,060
 To partner with the Holy Spirit

311
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:31,540
 to see more hope and joy and peace and life

312
00:14:31,540 --> 00:14:34,340
 come into the world is sacramental.

