00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:25,480
 "Like newborn babies, crave pure spiritual milk,

443
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:28,140
 "so that by it you may grow up,"

444
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:31,020
 notice this, "grow up in your salvation.

